    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "District Health Systems are more effective in delivering quality PHC\r\n\r\n\tPHC services strengthened\r\n\r\n\tCapacity MOHP in Health Policy and Planning is improved\r\n\r\n\tNational guidelines and monographs on Ayurveda in PHC developed\r\n\r\n\tCapacity of MOHP to implement NHSP-2  is strengthened\r\n\r\n\tCapacity building to strengthen HSIS implemented\r\n\r\n\tCapacity of NEPHEIN member institutions to advance Public Health / Primary Health Care through District Health Systems Development is supported\r\n\r\n\tCapacity of HE&FM unit increased to provide economic analysis and advice for NHSP-2 implemetnation\r\n\r\n\tPatient safety piloted\r\n\r\n\tNHA disseminated\r\n\r\n\tNepal Health Research Council capacity +to assess Health Systems strengthened\r\n\r\n\tStrengthened Health Library through updated knowledge, information and services to the HELLIS participants libraries with latest books, journals and electronic materials\r\n\r\n\tImplementation of National Drug Policies improved\r\n\r\n\tRegulatory oversight of the DDA strengthened\r\n\r\n\tThe development of a HR strategy, projection and action plan is supported\r\n\r\n\tCapacity of National Professional Councils (NMC, NNC, NHPC) for accreditation, licenising and representing their members is enhanced"
      },
      "ne": null
    },
